   0:   aload_0
   1:   getfield        #1; //Field i:I
   4:   ireturn
  LineNumberTable:
   line 1: 0
  Synthetic: true

}

So, there is a line number table with just one entry in for the generated method
(and it is marked synthetic) - I guess we should do the same for AspectJ
generated methods !

